messageBody:
>--- "ljb114ca" <ljb114ca@y...> wrote:
>> Can some give me a liitle suggestions how to solve the
>> Eight Queens problem with TDD metod?
>
> Start with one queen -- on a 1x1 board.

It might be helpful to have a function to ask...

'Is this a valid configuration of 2 queens on a 2x2 board?'
"Q.",
".Q"
(No.)

'Is this?'
"Q....",
"...Q.",
".Q...",
"....Q",
"..Q.."
(Yes.)
